
CONTRAST SECURITY OPENSHIFT DEMO

contrast-openshift-s2i-java

DESCRIPTION

A demonstration of how to use the Java agent in conjunction with Openshift S2i image creation.

USAGE

s2i build git@github.com:Contrast-Security-OSS/vulnerable-spring-boot-application.git contrast/contrast-openshift-s2i-java --runtime-artifact=/opt/app-root/src/target --runtime-image=contrast/contrast-s2i-jre vulnerable-spring-boot-application

ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES

* CONTRAST_API_KEY
* CONTRAST_URL
* CONTRAST_AUTHORIZATION
* CONTRAST_ORGANIZATION_ID

